[`scale`](/vi/guides/yolo-data-augmentation#scale-scale)| 0.562| 0.9| 0.95| 0.95| 0.95  
[`fliplr`](/vi/guides/yolo-data-augmentation#flip-left-right-fliplr)| 0.606| 0.304| 0.304| 0.304| 0.304  
[`degrees`](/vi/guides/yolo-data-augmentation#rotation-degrees)| 1.11| ~0| ~0| ~0| ~0  
[`shear`](/vi/guides/yolo-data-augmentation#shear-shear)| 1.46| ~0| ~0| ~0| ~0  
